page.title: 14Halesworth Clubs
page.content: In Halesworth 1985 the sports facilities we have are;the Halesworth Playing Field,the Angel Bowls club, Hockey club,Football club and the Maltings Lesuire club.The Charity clubs we have are;the Rotary club,the Royal British Legion,Probus club,Womans Royal Voluntary Service,Meals on Wheels,Beech House and the Womans Institute.The Teenage clubs we have are;the Youth club,Scouts,Cubs,Guides,Brownies,Young Farmers,Circle '67 (drama group) and Army Cadets.Other clubs are;Gardeners Society,Movie Film Society,Over 60's club and Arthritas and Rheumatism Committee.
